name: Northern Lights
description: Classic. It was one of the first hybrids to gain popularity due to the high resin production and the short flowering time of Indica strains. The genetics they propagated came from indigenous Afghani landrace, and it was selectively bred and backcrossed. Because of the prohibition, gardens were forced to go indoors, outside the law. Strains with higher yields in less space and time were needed. That was one of the main strains in grower´s resistance history. We resist, love it´s gonna flourish and break ignorance like a herb that grows above concrete. Peace.
